{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "lt-atgame-api-collection",
    "name": "LT-ATGAME External APIs",
    "description": "API Collection สำหรับทดสอบ Deposit และ Share APIs",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://api.ruaysud.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "00EBAAA48032C118787BD5E7C09C7AF12FA1766F3874C933FC2FBBA928ED65F4",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "line_id",
      "value": "YOUR_LINE_USER_ID",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "line_at",
      "value": "@lottwin88",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Deposit",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Deposit Data",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "api-key",
                "value": "{{api_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/players/v1/line/deposit?line_id={{line_id}}&line_at={{line_at}}&start_date={{start_date}}&end_date={{end_date}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["players", "v1", "line", "deposit"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "line_id",
                  "value": "{{line_id}}",
                  "description": "LINE User ID (เช่น U1234567890abcdef)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "line_at",
                  "value": "{{line_at}}",
                  "description": "LINE AT identifier (@lottwin88)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "start_date",
                  "value": "{{start_date}}",
                  "description": "Unix timestamp วันเริ่มต้น (เช่น 1703404800)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "end_date",
                  "value": "{{end_date}}",
                  "description": "Unix timestamp วันสิ้นสุด (เช่น 1703491200)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "ดึงข้อมูลยอดฝากเงินของผู้ใช้ในช่วงระยะเวลาที่กำหนด\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"deposit\": 750\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success Response",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/players/v1/line/deposit?line_id=U1234567890&line_at=@lottwin88&start_date=1703404800&end_date=1703491200"
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"deposit\": 750\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Share (Affiliate)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Affiliate Data",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "API-KEY",
                "value": "{{api_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/games/players/line/affiliate?line_id={{line_id}}&line_at={{line_at}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["games", "players", "line", "affiliate"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "line_id",
                  "value": "{{line_id}}",
                  "description": "LINE User ID (เช่น U1234567890abcdef)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "line_at",
                  "value": "{{line_at}}",
                  "description": "LINE AT identifier (@lottwin88)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "ดึงข้อมูล Affiliate (การแชร์) ของผู้ใช้\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"ABC123\",\n  \"playerBets\": [\n    {\n      \"username\": \"user1\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2025-11-01T10:00:00Z\",\n      \"bet_amount\": 100,\n      \"commission_amount\": 10\n    }\n  ],\n  \"playerSummaries\": [\n    {\n      \"date\": \"2025-11-01\",\n      \"amount\": 100\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success Response",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/games/players/line/affiliate?line_id=U1234567890&line_at=@lottwin88"
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": \"ABC123\",\n  \"playerBets\": [\n    {\n      \"username\": \"user1\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2025-11-01T10:00:00Z\",\n      \"bet_amount\": 100,\n      \"commission_amount\": 10\n    }\n  ],\n  \"playerSummaries\": [\n    {\n      \"date\": \"2025-11-01\",\n      \"amount\": 100\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Set default timestamps if not provided",
          "if (!pm.variables.get('start_date')) {",
          "    // Default: start of today",
          "    const today = new Date();",
          "    today.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);",
          "    pm.variables.set('start_date', Math.floor(today.getTime() / 1000));",
          "}",
          "",
          "if (!pm.variables.get('end_date')) {",
          "    // Default: end of today",
          "    const today = new Date();",
          "    today.setHours(23, 59, 59, 999);",
          "    pm.variables.set('end_date', Math.floor(today.getTime() / 1000));",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
